{"tid":1858822,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國鑑證科警員證實   Android 手機較 iPhone 更難破解","createTime":"2020-02-03T02:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T08:05:06.000Z","uid":1886,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d7249b0480c44d55a9b9a04baea16e34f42fa1d2","tid":1858822,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:34:51.000Z","msg":"智能手機裝著不少個人資料和通訊記錄，當執法機關需要進行調查時，往往都會從疑犯的智能手機入手。近期有不少新聞與 iPhone 被執法機關破解有關，日前有美國負責數碼鑑證的警員就透露，現時的 Android 手機比 iPhone 更難破解。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/02/03/android-encryption-forensics/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F02%2F03%2Fandroid-encryption-forensics%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7VxvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=4d1fdce6\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/02/03/android-encryption-forensics/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"b07d72a8abc442506f91f766f479a6726174c676","tid":1858822,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:35:08.000Z","msg":"來自德州 Fort Worth 警區的數碼鑑證探員 Rex Kiser 接受訪問時，表示他們約一年前無法破解 iPhone，但可以破解任何 Android 手機，但現在並非所有 Android 手機都能破解。報導提到執法機構僱用專業的手機破解公司，當中最出名的 Cellebrite 擁有能夠破解包括 iPhone X 在內手機的工具，它能夠抓住 GPS 位置、訊息、通話記錄、聯絡人資訊，甚至 Instagram、Twitter、LinkedIn 等程式的數據，有助進行檢控工作。"},{"pid":"6817e84f82c28eb50f5b6e770eb4ccb8bfbda404","tid":1858822,"uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:35:36.000Z","msg":"報導指 Cellebrite 的工具在對付 Android 手機的加密技術，就未如 iPhone 般成功，例如 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Google Pixel 2、Samsung Galaxy S9、華為 P20 Pro</strong></span></span> 都不對應，無法取得社交媒體、瀏覽或 GPS 資料。雖然 Cellebrite 的工具在 Android 層面比較遜色，但並不代表 Android 無從破解，只是花費的時間和資源較多。"},{"pid":"fd47b22994690da0aadf95f25d4d8bbbe1158915","tid":1858822,"uid":11420,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:36:06.000Z","msg":"可能係因為Android市佔率低 無人開發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2563937588d0ec2575d324d97049f95c6efeceb3","tid":1858822,"uid":261773,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:37:23.000Z","msg":"你問個差佬佢破解唔到咩機，信得過咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a427354248d5b6e440905b380ab225332b5ee883","tid":1858822,"uid":239086,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"fd47b22994690da0aadf95f25d4d8bbbe1158915","tid":1858822,"uid":11420,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:36:06.000Z","msg":"可能係因為Android市佔率低 無人開發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:37:37.000Z","msg":"碎片化，就算一個普通app都未必可以完全支援晒所有機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c9b8fefd26c45442d3d0faaea2c2ced8f92ae2","tid":1858822,"uid":245849,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fd47b22994690da0aadf95f25d4d8bbbe1158915","tid":1858822,"uid":11420,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:36:06.000Z","msg":"可能係因為Android市佔率低 無人開發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:39:03.000Z","msg":"識電腦唔會咁講......<br />\n<br />\n主要係Apple不思進取，安全性一直冇點進步過。"},{"pid":"728687c0212eb9053b165377986a04b74ba90ad6","tid":1858822,"uid":125488,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:39:48.000Z","msg":"講得出iphone安全呢啲白痴野既<br />\n你都唔會預佢哋會好理性咁回答你個post架啦"},{"pid":"b61f9701babe30470aa2a3b0d6d2e87b0b142bdd","tid":1858822,"uid":240336,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"fd47b22994690da0aadf95f25d4d8bbbe1158915","tid":1858822,"uid":11420,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:36:06.000Z","msg":"可能係因為Android市佔率低 無人開發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:41:59.000Z","msg":"你知唔知 iphone 個市佔率有幾多的？"},{"pid":"8d1e20d8beb7b0c831a07488675d5626467b3dfb","tid":1858822,