":"可能係因為Android市佔率低 無人開發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:53:16.000Z","msg":"無常識唔好出黎獻醜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50bec25a16645fb63b80f0b977301cb4a151e1e","tid":1858822,"uid":44718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd47b22994690da0aadf95f25d4d8bbbe1158915","tid":1858822,"uid":11420,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:36:06.000Z","msg":"可能係因為Android市佔率低 無人開發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:55:46.000Z","msg":"7成都低, 咁點先算高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba41c5967fc30a09529d041f93e5590be72c0420","tid":1858822,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:56:17.000Z","msg":"喬布斯死左之後 iphone只係一件垃圾 狗都不屌"},{"pid":"040df0ef112b157f4616621c3d834604141d3085","tid":1858822,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T03:06:46.000Z","msg":"If you own one of those Android phones just mentioned or even newer phones from those same companies, don&rsquo;t think that your phone is uncrackable. <span style=\"color: red;\">Just because Cellebrite&rsquo;s tool doesn&rsquo;t work doesn&rsquo;t mean investigators can&rsquo;t extract the data they need</span><br />\n<br />\n部機用唔到落某部分android 機咋喎，冇其他tool嘅咩<br />\n<br />\n最安全用番Feature phone"},{"pid":"e0acd75218410b9d4ae4f71751a58cae933408ae","tid":1858822,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0345d4f98d5d96dbbcf853cfbecf58c572cd6938","tid":1858822,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:51:29.000Z","msg":"美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d1a163e66210dde7531ec7b5d20c555e68f5e2","tid":1858822,"uid":53857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:54:40.000Z","msg":"Android可能比iPhone安全<br />\n但屌米同屎為個堆支那出既Android機就一定唔撚係<br />\nd資料全部送中，支共解都唔洗解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8545f0ca4f59ae2828f186365360eb2e8cb828e5","tid":1858822,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />an機講update唔同款都唔知幾耐 IOS 一出就立刻有update"},{"pid":"c524f239990644bb375308df7af66cb7ac248fde","tid":1858822,"uid":131691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8545f0ca4f59ae2828f186365360eb2e8cb828e5","tid":1858822,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />an機講update唔同款都唔知幾耐 IOS 一出就立刻有update"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T05:01:05.000Z","msg":"有update唔等於secure<br />\n唯一真正能夠保證secure嘅方法係成部機，由軟件到硬件，全部嘅源碼都係開源，跟住全世界嘅IT人同黑客一齊搵漏洞<br />\n<br />\n但係至今仍然冇一部咁嘅機<br />\n呢個係最大問題<br />\n執行高危行動時，用高危行動先會開嘅機，或甚至feature phone啦"},{"pid":"5c43173be91475061405c391baf8b465e2df4b40","tid":1858822,"uid":291803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T05:10:10.000Z","msg":"破唔破解到好在乎間電話公司既配合<br />\n不過可以話比你知要解iphone一定難過android<br />\n利申 做鑑證 非狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee8064e372ab138ef3ba772feec8080cb38ccff2","tid":1858822,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T08:05:06.000Z","msg":"推"}]}